01:01:42.430 --> 01:01:44.390
But you're twice as likely to
come out with the correct

01:01:44.390 --> 01:01:46.930
answer when you go with your
best possible answer.

01:01:46.930 --> 01:01:48.940
So that people who crossed out
their answers or erased their

01:01:48.940 --> 01:01:51.270
answers, they were twice as
likely to move to a good

01:01:51.270 --> 01:01:54.770
answer than leave behind
a good answer.

01:01:54.770 --> 01:01:56.084
Yeah?

